00050 static void rna_def_timeline_marker(BlenderRNA *brna)
00051 {
00052     StructRNA *srna;
00053     PropertyRNA *prop;
00054 
00055     srna = RNA_def_struct(brna, "TimelineMarker", NULL);
00056     RNA_def_struct_sdna(srna, "TimeMarker");
00057     RNA_def_struct_ui_text(srna, "Marker", "Marker for noting points in the timeline");
00058 
00059     /* String values */
00060     prop = RNA_def_property(srna, "name", PROP_STRING, PROP_NONE);
00061     RNA_def_property_ui_text(prop, "Name", "");
00062     RNA_def_struct_name_property(srna, prop);
00063     RNA_def_property_update(prop, 0, "rna_TimelineMarker_update");
00064 
00065     prop = RNA_def_property(srna, "frame", PROP_INT, PROP_TIME);
00066     RNA_def_property_ui_text(prop, "Frame", "The frame on which the timeline marker appears");
00067     RNA_def_property_update(prop, 0, "rna_TimelineMarker_update");
00068 
00069     prop = RNA_def_property(srna, "select", PROP_BOOLEAN, PROP_NONE);
00070     RNA_def_property_boolean_sdna(prop, NULL, "flag", 1 /*SELECT*/);
00071     RNA_def_property_ui_text(prop, "Select", "Marker selection state");
00072     RNA_def_property_update(prop, 0, "rna_TimelineMarker_update");
00073 
00074 #ifdef DURIAN_CAMERA_SWITCH
00075     prop = RNA_def_property(srna, "camera", PROP_POINTER, PROP_NONE);
00076     RNA_def_property_struct_type(prop, "Object");
00077     RNA_def_property_flag(prop, PROP_EDITABLE|PROP_ID_SELF_CHECK);
00078     RNA_def_property_ui_text(prop, "Camera", "Camera this timeline sets to active");
00079 #endif
00080 }
